Category:Military personnel of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: Asset I-32 was a member of the intelligence network that served the independent operative known as the Shroud during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. I-32 served in the Imperial Military, but around 3637 BBY, I-32 was unexpectedly reassigned to a frontline posting and quickly killed in battle, and the asset's death prompted the Shroud to send Asset I-4 to investigate.
